data.title: Robert Black
data.meta_description: Jake Rubendall is an Associate with Lee & Associates - North San Diego County office in Carlsbad and has been with the Williams Roth Group since 2018. He specializes in representing landlords, tenants, sellers, and buyers for industrial, office, R&D, flex, and land properties throughout San Diego County.
data.text:
Robert has been working in commercial real estate since graduating from the business school at the University of Colorado at Boulder in 1996. He has focused on senior housing and alternative investments.

Robert has years of experience in the sector and has been involved in the acquisition, disposition, and financing of over $3 billion in total consideration of senior housing and alternative investments.
